===Adjective===
{{en-adj}}

# {{mathematics}} Proper to be [[add]]ed; [[positive]]; -- opposed to [[subtractive]].
# Of or pertaining to [[addition]].

====Antonyms====
* [[subtractive]]

====Derived terms====
* [[additive function]]
* [[additive inverse]]
* [[additive identity]]
